Employment
Coyote Ugly Saloon Application
Coyote Ugly Saloon is looking for bartenders, security, and barbacks!
All staff must be 21 or older.
Bartenders must be able to pour a drink, keep a beat and look good doing it. Dancing, singing, and bartending experience preferred, but we will train the right applicants.
